{#
  Base template for every extractor under extractors/<kind>/extractor.j2.

  Required vars (provided by prompts.py via --json-vars):
    kind                string — the extractor kind name
    output_path         string — absolute path the agent must write
    source_text_path    string — converted source markdown path
    quintet_path        string — path to the package-local quintet.yaml vocabulary
    container_metadata  string|object|null — convert-stage metadata,
                                              null for tasks pre-convert
    quintet             object|null         — classified quintet,
                                              null for the classify task
    topic               string|null         — classified topic, null
                                              for the classify task

  Required overrides in child templates:
    {% block instructions %}  — kind-specific extraction instructions
    {% block builder_calls %} — `curator.sh builders add ...` calls;
                                content goes UNDER the shared
                                "### 2. Set fields per the schema"
                                header that the base provides.

  Optional overrides:
    {% block source_paths %}  — extra upstream paths beyond the defaults
                                (used by summary/compose which read upstream
                                outputs and verdicts)
    {% block extras %}        — content placed after the OUTPUT block

  All children get security-frame.md.j2 prepended automatically.
#}
